detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

DESCRIPTION:
============
An EXQUISITELY finished and well detailed,,spacious,neat and worthy of mention cosy&homely,affordable and fully serviced (apartment) room self contained ( especially considering how alarming rents of non-serviced letting or apartments are on the real estate market now and how more than 1year rent are demanded for most of them). It's,located within one of the hearts of yaba central. It makes for a easy connect to unilag road,herbert macaulay or iyana oworo express way(as a worker looking to swiftly connect all parts of the islands and mainlands). The house is newly remodeled and integrated with modern good facilities. It's located in an ideal and safe part of the area, which leaves you feeling relaxed and comfortable.
IT'S A FUSION of solid real estate architecture, with a touch of elegance,beauty,comfort and 21st century style.
YOU ARE SURE TO LOVE and BE CAPTIVATED BY IT.
INTERIOR FEATURES
=================
*Spacious room fully screed walls and P. O. P ceiling with floor fully and nicely glazed tilied plus stylish movable wardrobe. *Room is well ventilated and furnished with Air conditioning system(A.C).
*Good,strong,stylish doors used in apartment.
*Kitchen is fitted with new&modern top and bottom cabinets
*Toilet and Bath are well tiled,with new wash hand basin,press on toilet seat,modern shower accessories/fittings and a hot and cold water heater.
*Room to be put in a PAY 'N' PACK-IN state.
EXTERIOR FEATURES:
=================
*24 hours or round the clock clean borehole water
*24 hours light/power with SOLAR PANELS connected to INVERTERS(for night light) and a noiseless power generating plant as backup for when NEPA light fails
*FULLY LIT and WALL SCREED HALLWAY with P.O.P ceiling with floor beautifully tiled all through.
*FULLY wall screed and tiled stairways.
*A LAUNDRY room with fully state of the art and functioning washing and drying machines for all residents and a pressing/ironing room.
*A recreation spot to unwind/relax and be sporty/athletic
*Building's common areas under surveillance with digital cctv cameras for that extra touch of security/caution which GOD All-Mighty Alone Provides.
*A beautiful and spacious reception and a waiting area for guest/visitors.
*Building is fenced round with strong security gates and parking space.
IT IS NOT A HOSTEL or HOTEL but a REAL ESTATE DELIGHT for the CIVILISED,CORPORATE MIND and BODY.

$N==Rent is 350k P.A x 1year rent only(and no more)==N$
Annual service charge covers; *FULL 24/7 electricity via NEPA,SOLAR+INVERTER and GENERATOR*Laundry Room,Ironing Room*Front Desk Receptionist services,Waiting room*Recreation/Relaxation spot*Uniformed security Guards*Lawma,Cleaning of compound.
ANNUAL SERVICE CHARGE is PAYABLE MONTHLY at 25k Per month.

detail_description:
DESCRIPTION
============
This is an elegantly finished,well detailed,Spacious and affordable FULY SERVICED and ENSUITE room self contained in a STRONG and MODERN LOOKING REAL ESTATE ARCHITECTURE (especially giving how alarming the rents of NON-SERVICED apartments are and how more than 1year rent are demanded for most of them too!!!),located within ONE OF THE HEARTS of Yaba CENTRAL.As a worker you can swiftly CONNECT to HERBERT MaCAULAY EXPRESS ROAD.The structure is NEWLY REMODELED to meet with 21st century building standards and it's strategically placed in a safe,ideal and easy to access part of the environment.
YOU WILL LOVE THIS ONE.
INDOOR FACILITIES:
================
*Spacious room fully screed walls and P.O.P ceiling with floor fully and nicely glazed tiled.
*Strong&stylish doors and Wardrobe used in apartment.
*Kitchen is relatively spacious,tiled and fitted with up-to-date wall and floor cabinets
*Toilet/Bath fully floor and wall tiled,with a cute wash hand basin,press on toilet seat,stylish shower fittings/accessories and NEW WATER HEATER.
*Painted room with COOL/MATURED COLORS and apartment to be in a PAY 'N' PACK IN STATE.
OUTDOOR FACILITIES:
==================
*24 hours clean borehole water.
*Building is SERVICED,so alternative light/electricity is enjoyed with the use of a POWER GENERATING PLANT as BACKUP during general power outage in the area.
*Beautiful HALLWAY and STAIRCASE with screed walls,P.O.P ceiling, with floor TILES all through.
*Building is fenced round with strong gates and parking space.
*Security guard present on property.
*Good and easy road networks to all major roads and expressway

ANNUAL RENT plus SERVICE CHARGE is 650k P.A x 1year only (not 1 and half or 2yrs).
ANNUAL SERVICE CHARGE covers: *EKEDC LIGHT*GENERATING SET ALTERNATIVE LIGHT*LAWMA for WASTE DISPOSAL*CLEANIBG COMPOUND plus COMMON AREAS*SECURITY FEE*WATER*EVACUATION ofxSEPTIC TANK etc.
CAUTION FEE: Yes.
Agreement and Commission: YES(please call for amount or % as APPLY).
N.B: Corporate or Working CLASS/ENTERPRENEUR WANTED PLS.
ONLY direct,serious & no delay or time wasting accommodation seekers should contact please.
INSPECTION AVAILABLE 7Days of the week(including sundays).
For Inspection bookings,pls call PHONE number or WHATSAPP

description: Mini flat in a serene environment
detail_description:
Mini flat on third floor is up for rent... So guys, here is the thing, its pretty straight forward, I'm moving to a bigger apartment and still have 5 months before my rent gets renewed. This lease is ideal for someone who is willing to THINK LONG TERM by doing away with the annoying and costly side of agreement and commission.

It's simple, just pay 150k for the remaining number of months left & @ the end of May 2020, you simply pay 400k (annual rent) to the landlord. I will introduce whoever takes over the mini flat to the landlord as a relative.

Now back to the accommodation itself, it's a mini flat ideal for a young professional, single or newly married. The house is located just behind Oyadiran Estate, Sabo. From the master bed, you get a good view of casino, alagomeji.

The mini flat has a small kitchen, a sitting room, two toilets, two bathrooms and a moderately sized balcony where you can spread your clothes and place your generator.

The flat has a newly installed submersible pump and borehole and the area averages 13-16 hrs of public electricity everyday. The house is 2 mins drive from sabo and 10 mins drive to Third mainland.

Kindly call to grab this unique opportunity.
